{"tid":1409562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"起身搭車啦","createTime":"2019-08-04T22:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T23:03:48.000Z","uid":5422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d41798bfa68f0686538fe30d3163ed83397899","tid":1409562,"uid":5422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:32:57.000Z","msg":"香港早晨 係時候準備搭地鐵了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4986c37685fcd45b5789dbab1f1f2d4fed492ee3","tid":1409562,"uid":5422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:34:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPjTYF7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPjTYF7.png&h=bc9686e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4R8JBsN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4R8JBsN.png&h=ba3b0c90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POs2R07.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOs2R07.png&h=aadf5edf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3714a71a4bf9d32474c431192ec6edbf9561238d","tid":1409562,"uid":20457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:42:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e701e492c77f5b49403b5b73dda81df7dddb083","tid":1409562,"uid":134054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:42:37.000Z","msg":"如果俾人插可以咁對答<br />\n➡️阻住我返工<br />\n❌粗口<br />\n⭕️我都好想返工啊<br />\n➡️阻住我哋啲市民/冇人支持你㗎<br />\n❌阻乜x嘢啊<br />\n⭕️支持警察執法（成立獨立調查委員會）<br />\n➡️你咪去攪林鄭囉，攪我地啲小市民做嘜？<br />\n⭕️係林鄭搞緊小市民<br />\n⭕️係囉，佢唔出黎喎，要求政府回應！佢月薪40萬咖<br />\n⭕️唔好搞人屋企咁冇品，人地都有屋企人，屋企人係無辜咖！<br />\n⭕️林鄭好多屋企，唔知佢訓邊<br />\n⭕️林鄭成個政府都冇鬼用，淨係識搵警察出黎打人，自己就匿埋，搞到愈來愈多人出黎示威<br />\n(將責任推俾政府，強調示威者都係被逼)<br />\n➡️本人撐你都變到唔撐啦<br />\n⭕️請你體諒，宜家每星期都有好多流血衝突，好多年輕人受重傷，咁落去香港就黎打仗乜都冇，堵錢堵路已經係最和平嘅方法去施壓俾政府<br />\n⭕️其實我哋而家唔係要爭取同意,係希望政府可以回應依家社會發生緊嘅嘢<br />\n⭕️你唔需要撐我，撐警察就得，支持成立獨立調査委員會😂<br />\n➡️成班死癈青，淨係識攪事<br />\n⭕️今日好多律師會計師公務員都罷工呀，政府太過分，天怒人怨<br />\n⭕️如果政府真係有做嘢就唔會咁多死癈青啦，收納税人咁多錢又唔做嘢，一日到黑只係識得譴責！<br />\n➡️粗口<br />\n❌粗口回應<br />\n⭕️嘩支持政府嘅人咁暴力嘅😱<br />\n⭕️嘩！問候我哋呢啲小市民<br />\n⭕️你與其責備我地搞事不如責備下呢個暴力制度嘅政府<br />\n⭕️我明嘅，你係想鬧個政府搞到啲人出黎示威<br />\n⭕️我都好嬲呀，講左咁多次訴求，政府都漠示民意<br />\n⭕️車長！有人講粗口，違反香港鐵路附例呀！罰佢$5000！"},{"pid":"d802b4db11b0aead254781d331f02817c1c51159","tid":1409562,"uid":5422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3714a71a4bf9d32474c431192ec6edbf9561238d","tid":1409562,"uid":20457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:42:06.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:42:37.000Z","msg":"食完早餐齊齊搭車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3afad61add318216b3684cb22d997c5ba99fd16","tid":1409562,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:42:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">起身啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我會罷工 配合不合作運動 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"d6ef323d1bd85b373fa008465598b51e86b06453","tid":1409562,"uid":5422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d72cb75f5d510a6bf5048f21f7545ad2a00c5f1","tid":1409562,"uid":5422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:03:48.000Z","msg":"［8.5］MTR 車長嚴正呼籲！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1408296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1408296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}